OL,6,FLater the inquiry saw a letter written
OL,7,Fby Frank Atherton, the Chief Medical
OL,8,FOfficer for Wales, to Dr Goodall which
OL,9,Fwas sent in August 2020. The letter
OL,10,Fraised concerns that Wales might not
OL,11,Fbe prepared for a second wave of
OL,12,Fcoronavirus.
