OL,15,Fbeen lifted and the first phase of the
OL,16,Fpandemic had passed.
OL,18,FDr Atherton wrote, "I am... writing to
OL,19,Fflag concerns about our ability to
OL,20,Fmanage the next phase of the pandemic
OL,21,Fin Wales.
