OL,6,F"The context for this is that
OL,7,Finfection rates are currently low and
OL,8,Fstable in the country but I fully
OL,9,Fexpect to see significant resurgence
OL,10,Fover the next few months in keeping
OL,11,Fwith international experience even
OL,12,Fwith our enhanced control measures."
OL,14,FThe letter went on to raise concerns
OL,15,Fabout the NHS staff's ability to
OL,16,Fwithstand to future outbreaks.
